Final lineup
* Sawao Yamanaka (山中 さわお, Yamanaka Sawao) – vocals, rhythm guitar 
* Yoshiaki Manabe (真鍋吉明, Manabe Yoshiaki) – lead guitar 
* Shinichiro Sato (佐藤信一郎, Sato Shin&#x27;ichirō) – drums 

Former members
* Kenji Ueda (上田ケンジ, Ueda Kenji) – bass 
Support members
* Tomoyuki Miyakawa - bass 
